  <brief_title>Does Administration of Probiotics During Infancy Increase the Caries Risk of a Child</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Administration of Bifidobacterium Lactis BB-12 and the Caries Occurence of Children a 4 Years of Age</official_title>
  <sponsors>
