  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim: to examine caries occurrence in children who ten years ago received a mixture of
      probiotics during infancy.

      Hypothesis: the administration of probiotics during infancy has no effect on future dental
      health.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
